commit.message:
Adds missing MIME application/wasm

When a simple web server is used, e.g.

     final HttpServer server = SimpleFileServer.createFileServer(ADDR, root, SimpleFileServer.OutputLevel.VERBOSE);

to serve .wasm files, it uses application/octet-stream instead
of application/octet-stream, making the browser to fall back to
a less favorable method of loading the file.
